\r\n**Actual behavior:** Incorrect handling of HTTP Header \"Accept\" when set to \"*/*\"\r\n\r\n### Versions\r\n\r\nUsing latest crystal and amber versions:\r\n```\r\nCrystal 0.24.1 (2017-12-22)\r\n\r\nLLVM: 4.0.0\r\nDefault target: x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu\r\n```\r\n```\r\nAmber CLI (amberframework.org) - v0.6.4\r\n```","score":1.0}]}
